<dl id="n53083q"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n53" href="#n53083q">N53 (VI.B.46)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n53all.htm#n53083q"> 83(q)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> murder, idolatry, adultery, / <font color="green">[??]</font> <font color="green">[??]</font> <font color="green">[??]</font>, <font color="green">[??]</font> </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: These are grave or &lsquo;mortal&rsquo; sins <font color="green">[colloquially, &lsquo;mortlers&rsquo;]</font>, as opposed to venial or trifling sins. There is an absolute non-negotiable obligation imposed by divine institution upon all Christians of confessing all mortal sins committed after Baptism. Those committed before Baptism, presumably, disappear in the wash.</mm> </dd></dl>
